.SH DESCRIPTION
.B lorem
is a Lorem Ipsum text generator that fetches placeholder text from an API server with support for multiple output formats including plain text, HTML, Markdown, and JSON. It provides configurable amounts of paragraphs or sentences with automatic formatting options for web development, documentation, and design workflows.
.PP
The script simplifies placeholder text generation by providing API-based Lorem Ipsum text generation, multiple output formats (text, HTML, markdown, JSON), configurable amounts of paragraphs and sentences, automatic line break insertion for sentences, file save capability with append support, mixed content generation (alternating sentences and paragraphs), silent mode for scripting and automation, and desktop notification integration for completion feedback.
.PP
lorem is particularly useful for web development placeholder content, design mockup text generation, documentation template creation, API testing with realistic text data, and automated content generation in build processes.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.BR paragraphs | p " " [\fI\,NUMBER\fR]
Generate specified number of paragraphs. Default: 5 paragraphs (LOREM_DEFAULT_AMOUNT_PARAGRAPH).
.TP
.BR sentences | s " " [\fI\,NUMBER\fR]
Generate specified number of sentences. Default: 15 sentences (LOREM_DEFAULT_AMOUNT_SENTENCE).
.TP
.BR amount | a " " [\fI\,NUMBER\fR]
Generate mixed content alternating between one sentence and one paragraph for the specified count. Useful for varied placeholder text.
.TP
.BR html
Set HTML output format mode before specifying type and amount.
.TP
.BR markdown
Set Markdown output format mode before specifying type and amount.
.TP
[\fI\,NUMBER\fR]
Generate default type (paragraphs) with specified number. Default: 10 paragraphs (LOREM_DEFAULT_AMOUNT).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-html
